    "East:Starting from north East corner of the hill top and turn towards the south and proceed upto Madhusudan nagar bus stop and turn towards west and proceed along 60ft narasimhanagarmadhavadhara road and turn towards south at Dr no 36-92-242 and proceed south towards Srinivasanagar and jayabharatnagar road continuing up to bapujinagarUPHC and turn towards East and proceed along the CC road up to Dr.no 36-92-400/3 and proceed along the hill top up to Dr.no.36-93-349 and turn towards south and proceed along the CC road up to dr no. 36-93- 333/1 and proceed along CC road till it meets NH-16at Nanna Cell point, Indiranagar 5. South:Starting from the above point i.e. Nanna Cell point, Indiranagar 5 and turns towards the west and runs along the NH 16 Road via Government Polytechnic College up to Southwest corner of Government Polytechnic College compound wall at Surya Nagar 1. West:Starting from the above point i.e Southwest corner of Government Polytechnic College compound wall turns towards north and runs along the West compound wall Government Polytechnic College and meets Anjaneya Swamy temple and runs along PR Gardens Road upto NGGOs Colony bus stop and turns towards East side at d.no 37-12-76 and runs along the 60 Feet road up to d.No 37-12-71/4 i. e, Southwest corner of CISF quarters boundary Wall and turns north side runs along CISF quarters West boundary Wall and reach APEPDCL substation and runs up to top of the hill. North:Starting from the above point turns towards East and runs along the top of the hill and meets the starting point i.e., northEast corner of the Hill top"
