  "east: the boundary commences at the north-eastern (ne) corner at vignana bharathi school junction,the boundary turns southward and proceeds along neelammavepachettu road via mgm school to meet leelamahal junction. south: starting from the south-east corner at leelamahaljunction,the boundary turns westward and proceeds along dolphin junction road to meet dolphin junction. west: starting from the south-west corner at dolphin junction, the boundary turns northward and proceeds along geeth sangeeth road to reach captain ramarao junction.from there, it passes along allipuram main road to meet kummari veedhi junction. north: starting from the north-west corner at kummari veedhijunction,the boundary turns eastward and proceeds along kummari veedhi road and it passes via sri kashyap school to meet neelammavepachettu road at starting point vignana bharathi school junction": 40,
  "east: the boundary commences at the north-eastern (ne) corner at allipuram junction, the boundary turns southward and proceeds along allipuram main road to meet captain ramarao junctio.from this point, the boundary proceeds along geeth sangeeth road to meet dolphin junction road at dolphin junction. south: starting from the south-east corner at dolphin junction, the boundary turns westward and proceeds along 75 feet road.from this point, the boundary proceeds along gangula gedda, alignment and crossing bowdara road along the gedda to meet port road west: starting from the south-west corner at port road, the boundary turns northward and proceeds along port road to meet gnanapuram road at convent junction. north: starting from the north-west corner at convent junction,the boundary turns eastward and proceeds along convent junction road to meet railway station junction.from this point, the boundary proceeds along south jail road to meet allipuram main road at starting point allipuram junction": 41,
